&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#level-29&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span id=&#34;level-29&#34;&gt;Level 29&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;An interesting level. Nothing useful in both web page and source code.&lt;/p&gt;
