&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#level-9&#34; class=&#34;header-anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span id=&#34;level-9&#34;&gt;Level 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The page is called &lt;code&gt;connect the dots&lt;/code&gt;, and there lies an interesting comment, &lt;code&gt;first+second=?&lt;/code&gt; followed by a bunch of numbers. Maybe these numbers are coordinates?&lt;/p&gt;
