&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight python hljs&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;gutter&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;headers = {&lt;span class=&#34;hljs-string&#34;&gt;&amp;apos;Authorization&amp;apos;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;hljs-string&#34;&gt;f&amp;quot;Basic &lt;span class=&#34;hljs-subst&#34;&gt;{cred.decode()}&lt;/span&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;hljs-string&#34;&gt;&amp;apos;Range&amp;apos;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&#34;hljs-string&#34;&gt;&amp;apos;bytes=1152983631-&amp;apos;&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The output was too much. Let&amp;apos;s take a look at the first 20 bytes of the output. The signature of file is always hiding there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight python hljs&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;gutter&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hljs-built_in&#34;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;(r.content[:&lt;span class=&#34;hljs-number&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;{&amp;apos;Connection&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;close&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;Content-Length&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;239733&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;Content-Range&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;bytes 1152983631-1153223363/2123456789&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;Content-Transfer-Encoding&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;binary&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;Content-Type&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;application/octet-stream&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;Date&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;Mon, 18 Apr 2022 14:30:03 GMT&amp;apos;, &amp;apos;Server&amp;apos;: &amp;apos;lighttpd/1.4.55&amp;apos;}&lt;br&gt;b&amp;apos;PK\x03\x04\x14\x00\t\x00\x08\x00;\xa7\xaa2\xac\xe5f\x14\xa9\x00&amp;apos;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;PK\x03\x04&lt;/code&gt; is the signature of a zip file. -&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ZIP_(file_format)#Design&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then we should save the output to a zip file and try to unzip it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight python hljs&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;gutter&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hljs-keyword&#34;&gt;with&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;hljs-built_in&#34;&gt;open&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&#34;hljs-string&#34;&gt;&amp;apos;assets/20.zip&amp;apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;hljs-string&#34;&gt;&amp;apos;wb&amp;apos;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&#34;hljs-keyword&#34;&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; f:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    f.write(r.content)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&amp;apos;s a &lt;code&gt;readme.txt&lt;/code&gt;. OK, we are in level 21 now.&lt;/p&gt;

